summary: KIM NAMJOON
body:
YOU’RE BEAUTIFUL

KIM NAMJOON

You looked at your hideous reflection in mirror. Or thats what you thought. You have never felt so insecure about yourself before. According to yourself you had a fine figure. Though not slim and completely perfect like those models. Thick thighs, big breast or hourglass like figure but you never felt like you were hideous.

Or maybe your boyfriend, Kim Namjoon had made you feel secure about yourself with all his love and affection he shows towards you. How he looks at you with such intense glare that it looks like he is trying to memorize each and every perfection and imperfection which were perfection for him. The way he says I love you to you like it means world to him. How he never fails to remind you that you are beautiful. The way he devour every part of your skin and touches them so delicately on those intense night where you both show each other your love and make your bodies one.

In short Namjoon never gave you a chance to feel insecure about you. But after seeing Hyera, his ex girlfriend, few weeks ago you started to think about yourself otherwise.

“I wonder how he fell in love with you. Never knew Namjoon lowered his standard for girlfriend. I was way better than you. But i dont think he will be with you for long time. He will come back to me.”

She was right though. She was perfect. You wondered why Namjoon left her. Now you can’t stop feeling sacred and can’t help but feel like you are not perfect for him. And the fact that he is in other country is not helping either.

What if I am not enough for him?

What if he gets tired of me?

What if he finds someone better than me?

These thoughts have been spamming your mind all those week. When you talked to Namjoon on video call he had noticed your change in demnour and how you were not your usual self. He asked you many time if you were okay but you always replied with

“I am fine.”

“Just had a bad day.”

“I am missing you alot. That’s it.”

You didn’t wanted him to feel petty for you. Or get fed up from you being insecure about you and leave you.

You were standing in your bathroom in front of your mirror crying your eyes out on your imperfections like previous nights when you heard the click of your front door indicating that someone has came. And you recognized who it was when you heard him call your name.

“Y/N. I am home.”

“In here Namjoon.” You said quickly wiping the evidence of your struggles. He came behind you and hugged you smiling but when he saw your puffy and red eyes his smile turned into a frown.

“Are you fine? Did something happened?” He said turning you around.

“No. I am fine.” You replied looking at your feet.

“Okay. I know something is up. I have asked you many times but you always reply me with I am fine. So tell me what it is. I won’t know if you won’t tell me anything.” He held your face in his hands and made you look at him.

You closed your eyes and released a big sigh. “I meet Hyera few weeks ago. And she told me how I was imperfect for you and you will fall out of love with me. And I think she is right. I don’t have a perfect body and my thighs are so…” Before you can say anything he interrupted you.

“No. She is not right. And she is no one to decided who I will love or hate.” He hugged you and continued. “I can’t believe that you have been suffering from all of this for past few weeks alone and I wasn’t there for you. But I want to tell you that you are perfect the way you are and nothing is going to change my love for you. Everyone have imperfections. No one is perfect. Not me, not you or anyone. But our imperfections are what make us unique and perfect in someone’s eyes. A moon have spots in it but still people look at it.” He broke the hug to look at you.

“You don’t need to be perfect for me to love you. Just be yourself because I fell in love with that strong,cheerful (Y/N) who brightens my day and never let’s darkness consume her. I love you.” He smiled showing his dimple which you wanted to pock but stopped yourself. You smiled back with tears falling from your eyes.

He kissed your tears away and looked at you with love and passion. “And I want to show you how much I love you and how you are perfect for me.” He picked you up bridal style and took you to your shared bedroom.

His every action showed you how much he loved you. The way his fingers danced on your skin, the intense gaze filled with love and passion, the way your lips fit together in a passionate kiss, the constant I love you rolling out of his mouth was enough to make you feel secure and believe that you are perfect for him just the way he is perfect for you.
